data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 2 story located in sought after Wentzville school district! The main floor features the Kitchen complete with stainless appliances, granite countertops and center island. there is also a sitting room with French doors which would make a great home office and also boasting a formal Dining Rm. Upstairs there is a nice media area and the Master Bedroom Suite features a large walk-in closet and beautiful Garden Tub! In the finished lower level, there is the 5th bedroom with its own bathroom and a built-in slide for playtime with the kiddos. All of this and also a 3 car garage! This one won't last! Make your showing appointment today!
